      <title>特朗普在佐治亚州的刑事案件因部分指控被撤销而缩小范围</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-12/trump-criminal-case-in-georgia-narrowed-as-some-counts-tossed</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周四，佐治亚州一名法官缩小了该州针对前总统试图推翻 2020 年大选结果的刑事案件范围，唐纳德·特朗普取得了法律胜利。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-12/trump-criminal-case-in-georgia-narrowed-as-some-counts-tossed</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 12 Sep 2024 21:28:06 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
